      <title>对于许多中国人来说，经济感觉正陷入衰退</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-china-economy-feels-like-it-is-recession-2024-01-17/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国公务员考试前一天晚上，张美乐焦急地在宿舍走廊里来回踱步，排练答案。回到房间后，她才发现自己一直在哭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/many-china-economy-feels-like-it-is-recession-2024-01-17/</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 17 Jan 2024 23:07:34 GMT</pubDate>
